msgstr "grid"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "网格搜索"
msgstr "グリッド検索"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "参数少、离散空间，穷举或粗网格。"
msgstr "パラメータはほとんどなく、離散空間。網羅的または粗いグリッド検索。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "montecarlo"
msgstr "montecarlo"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "蒙特卡洛随机采样"
msgstr "モンテカルロランダムサンプリング"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "参数较多时随机抽样评估。"
msgstr "パラメータが多い場合はランダムサンプリング。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "GA"
msgstr "GA"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "遗传算法"
msgstr "遺伝的アルゴリズム"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "中高维、连续/离散混合。"
msgstr "中～高次元。連続/離散混合空間。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "SA"
msgstr "SA"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "模拟退火"
msgstr "模擬焼鈍"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "中维、易陷入局部最优时。"
msgstr "中程度の寸法。局所最適化が懸念される場合に役立ちます。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "PSO"
msgstr "PSO"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "粒子群优化"
msgstr "粒子群の最適化"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "连续空间、多峰。"
msgstr "複数の頂点を持つ連続した空間。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "bayesian"
msgstr "bayesian"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "贝叶斯优化"
msgstr "ベイズ最適化"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "样本昂贵、需少步数寻优。"
msgstr "高価な評価。いくつかのステップで良い結果が必要です。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:20
msgid "优化运行参数完整列表（罗列并简短解释）"
msgstr "最適化実行パラメータの完全なリスト (簡単な説明付き)"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "参数名"
msgstr "パラメータ"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "类型/可选值"
msgstr "タイプ/値"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "opti_method"
msgstr "opti_method"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "str"
msgstr "str"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "优化算法：grid、montecarlo、GA、SA、PSO、bayesian 等。"
msgstr ""
"最適化アルゴリズム: ``grid``, ``montecarlo``, ``GA``, ``SA``, ``PSO``, ``bayesian`` "
"など。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "opti_sample_count"
msgstr "opti_sample_count"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "int"
msgstr "int"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "采样/迭代次数（如蒙特卡洛样本数、遗传代数等）。"
msgstr "サンプル/反復の数 (例: モンテカルロ サンプルまたは GA 生成)。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "opti_output_count"
msgstr "opti_output_count"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "保留的最优结果数量（Top-K）。"
msgstr "保持する最良の結果の数 (Top-K)。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "目标函数相关"
msgstr "目的関数"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "—"
msgstr "—"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "如优化目标为夏普、回撤等，以配置或 API 为准。"
msgstr "例: シャープレシオまたはドローダウン。構成または API ドキュメントを参照してください。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "约束相关"
msgstr "制約"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md
msgid "若有约束（如最大回撤上限），以配置为准。"
msgstr "制約が適用される場合 (最大ドローダウン制限など)、構成を参照してください。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:30
msgid "回测区间、asset_pool 等与 mode=1 相同的参数在 mode=2 时同样生效。"
msgstr ""
"バックテストの日付範囲、``asset_pool``, and other arguments shared with ``mode=1`` also "
"apply in ``mode=2``。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:32
msgid "参数空间"
msgstr "パラメータ空間"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:34
msgid ""
"策略的 **Parameter** 及 **par_range** 定义优化时的搜索空间；框架按 opti_method 在该空间内采样或搜索。"
msgstr ""
"戦略は **``Parameter``** objects and **``par_range``** define the search space;"
" the framework samples or searches within it according to ``opti_method``。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:36
msgid "最小可运行示例"
msgstr "最小限の実行可能な例"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:47
msgid "配置要点"
msgstr "構成のハイライト"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:49
msgid "**回测区间、资产池**：与 mode=1 一致，决定每次参数评估的回测环境。"
msgstr "**バックテスト範囲と資産プール**: ``mode=1`` と同じ。これらは、各パラメーター評価のバックテスト環境を定義します。"

#: ../../source/optimization/2. run_optimization.md:50
msgid "**目标函数**：决定“更优”的定义（如夏普最大化、回撤最小化），影响排序与最终选取。"
msgstr ""
"**目的関数**: 「より良い」とは何を意味するのか (シャープを最大化する、ドローダウンを最小化するなど) "
"を定義し、ランキングと最終的な選択に影響を与えます。"
